492
00:43:37,026 --> 00:43:38,121
Yi Hyun!

493
00:43:44,066 --> 00:43:45,161
Sae Bom.

494
00:43:47,665 --> 00:43:48,961
Seninle olduğum için

495
00:43:51,366 --> 00:43:53,030
